    "body": "# fix(docsearch): upgrade to v4\r\n\r\nCloses #475\r\n\r\n## Problem\r\n\r\nThe site loads DocSearch v3 (`@docsearch/css@3`, `@docsearch/js@3`). The v3 docs link in the source comments (`.../docs/docsearch-v3/`) is dead, and v4 is now released.\r\n\r\n## Solution\r\n\r\nBump `@docsearch/css` and `@docsearch/js` from `@3` to `@4`, and fix the stale doc-link comments to point at `.../docs/docsearch`.\r\n\r\nThe `docsearch()` init is unchanged (v4 keeps the same `container`/`appId`/`apiKey`/`indexName` API), and the CSS overrides in `static/css/main.css` still apply since v4 retains the `DocSearch-*` classes and `--docsearch-*` variables.\r\n\r\n## Changes\r\n\r\n- `layouts/baseof.html`: `css@3` to `css@4`, `js@3` to `js@4`, fixed 2 doc-link comments\r\n- `layouts/_partials/nav.html`: fixed 1 doc-link comment\r\n\r\n## Verification\r\n\r\nBuilt and served locally with Hugo 0.162.1, then tested search in a headless browser:\r\n\r\n- both v4 assets return 200\r\n- search button renders, modal opens, returns results\r\n- Neovim theme intact, no visual regression vs v3\r\n",
    "closed_at": "2026-06-10T23:14:39Z",
